document_loader.py – Load & extract text from PDF, DOCX, TXT

embed_and_store.py – Split into chunks, generate embeddings, store in FAISS with metadata

vector_store.py – Save/load FAISS index

llm.py – Set up local LLM via llama-cpp-python

rag_engine.py – Embed query → retrieve top-k chunks → generate answer using context

main.py – Interactive CLI to run RAG